## 📌 Project Overview

This project turns an **ESP32 microcontroller** into a WiFi-connected PIR motion alarm you can monitor and control remotely from your phone using the [Blynk IoT](https://blynk.cloud) platform.

When motion is detected:
- ✅ The **relay fires immediately** — even without internet
- ✅ Blynk sends a **push notification** to your phone
- ✅ Blynk sends an **email alert**

