## ✨ Features

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| 🚶 Motion Detection | PIR sensor with configurable hold time |
| 📴 Offline Operation | Relay triggers without WiFi |
| 🔁 WiFi Auto-Fallback | Tries primary, instantly switches to backup network |
